release.name: End of HackUIowa 2019!
release.body:
# PFD for Android 1.0

Release of personal flight display application after HackUIowa 2019.

Download the APK [here](https://easterniowasound.com/PFD_for_Android) or find it attached to the release.

## Features
### Primary Flight Display
- Magnetic Heading Indicator
- Pitch Indicator
- Roll Indicator
- Altimeter
- Artifical Horizon
